    Models a constant-load instruction in the code array of a Code attribute, including "intrinsic constant" instructions (e.g., aload_0), "argument constant" instructions (e.g., bipush), and "load constant" instructions (e.g., LDC).

    Models an "argument constant" instruction (e.g., bipush).
